@node config "Easy Quake Configuration"


 @{b}Easy Quake Configuration@{ub}

 The keyfile has been removed and EZQuake will be freeware as of version 1.0.3.
 So if you are upgrading it is safe to delete the obsolete s:ezquake.key file.


 @{b}Tooltypes@{ub}


        Following MUST be present ! If not the default "Work:Quake" and
        "Quake" is used.
 
 
        QUAKEDIR=<your quake game dir>

                fe. QUAKEDIR=Work:Games/QuakePPC

        QUAKEEXEC=<your quake executable>
 
                fe. QUAKEEXEC=QuakeWOS
        
           
